snippet.textDisplay:
Czennies, we need your help!
NCT 127 is nominated as the Champion song of the 3rd week of March on Show Champion. To win we need to vote for them on Idol Champ.
You just need to download the app (Idol Champ), log in and vote. You can vote 3 times per day, so you'll need 9 chamsims (hearts) per day. You can collect them watching ads, leaving a comment on the community of NCT 127, commenting under a fandom ad fund or answering quizzes (you can find the answer on Twitter @/onlyquizanswers).
Also, please collect votes for The Show™, for this, you need to download the app "Starplay". You can collect 5 votes (50 silver stars token) per hour by watching ads, and also you can complete missions to have more silver stars (please make sure to convert your stars to votes before the 15th of each month or you will loose them).
Thanks :)

snippet.textDisplay:
Nctzens, we need your help!

NCT 127 is nominated as the Champion song of the 3rd week of March on Show Champion. To win we need to vote for them on Idol Champ.

You just need to download the app (Idol Champ), log in and vote. You can vote 3 times per day, so you'll need 9 chamsims (hearts) per day. You can collect them watching ads, leaving a comment on the community of NCT 127, commenting under a fandom ad fund or answering quizzes (you can find the answer on Twitter @/onlyquizanswers).

Also, please collect votes for The Show™, for this, you need to download the app "Starplay". You can collect 5 votes (50 silver stars token) per hour by watching ads, and also you can complete missions to have more silver stars (please make sure to convert your stars to votes before the 15th of each month or you will loose them).

Thanks you ♡
